{
  "title": "Self-Healing Shadow – SRE Copilot Dashboard",
  "description": "Autonomous SRE Agent monitoring: auth-service health, Bedrock LLM traces, and live postmortem feed.",
  "layout_type": "free",
  "is_read_only": false,
  "notify_list": [],
  "template_variables": [
    {
      "name": "env",
      "prefix": "env",
      "default": "hackathon"
    },
    {
      "name": "service",
      "prefix": "service",
      "default": "auth-service"
    }
  ],
  "widgets": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "definition": {
        "type": "timeseries",
        "title": "🔴 System Health – auth-service HTTP 5xx Error Rate & Latency",
        "title_size": "16",
        "title_align": "left",
        "show_legend": true,
        "legend_layout": "auto",
        "legend_columns": ["avg", "min", "max", "value"],
        "requests": [
          {
            "formulas": [
              {
                "alias": "HTTP 5xx Error Rate (%)",
                "formula": "query1"
              }
            ],
            "queries": [
              {
                "name": "query1",
                "data_source": "metrics",
                "query": "sum:trace.servlet.request.errors{env:$env,service:$service}.as_rate() / sum:trace.servlet.request.hits{env:$env,service:$service}.as_rate() * 100"
              }
            ],
            "response_format": "timeseries",
            "style": {
              "palette": "warm",
              "line_type": "solid",
              "line_width": "normal"
            },
            "display_type": "line"
          },
          {
            "formulas": [
              {
                "alias": "p99 Latency (ms)",
                "formula": "query2"
              }
            ],
            "queries": [
              {
                "name": "query2",
                "data_source": "metrics",
                "query": "p99:trace.servlet.request{env:$env,service:$service}"
              }
            ],
            "response_format": "timeseries",
            "style": {
              "palette": "cool",
              "line_type": "solid",
              "line_width": "normal"
            },
            "display_type": "line",
            "on_right_yaxis": true
          },
          {
            "formulas": [
              {
                "alias": "Request Throughput (req/s)",
                "formula": "query3"
              }
            ],
            "queries": [
              {
                "name": "query3",
                "data_source": "metrics",
                "query": "sum:trace.servlet.request.hits{env:$env,service:$service}.as_rate()"
              }
            ],
            "response_format": "timeseries",
            "style": {
              "palette": "grey",
              "line_type": "dashed",
              "line_width": "thin"
            },
            "display_type": "bars"
          }
        ],
        "yaxis": {
          "include_zero": true,
          "scale": "linear",
          "label": "Error Rate / Throughput"
        },
        "right_yaxis": {
          "include_zero": true,
          "scale": "linear",
          "label": "Latency (ms)"
        },
        "markers": [
          {
            "value": "y > 5",
            "display_type": "error dashed",
            "label": "Error threshold 5%"
          }
        ],
        "time": {
          "live_span": "1h"
        }
      },
      "layout": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0,
        "width": 8,
        "height": 4
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "definition": {
        "type": "timeseries",
        "title": "🤖 Agent LLM Trace – Bedrock Latency & Token Usage (ddtrace)",
        "title_size": "16",
        "title_align": "left",
        "show_legend": true,
        "legend_layout": "auto",
        "legend_columns": ["avg", "max", "value"],
        "requests": [
          {
            "formulas": [
              {
                "alias": "LLM p99 Latency (ms)",
                "formula": "query_llm_latency"
              }
            ],
            "queries": [
              {
                "name": "query_llm_latency",
                "data_source": "metrics",
                "query": "p99:aws.bedrock.invocation.latency{service:sre-agent-ecs}"
              }
            ],
            "response_format": "timeseries",
            "style": {
              "palette": "purple",
              "line_type": "solid",
              "line_width": "normal"
            },
            "display_type": "line"
          },
          {
            "formulas": [
              {
                "alias": "Input Tokens (avg)",
                "formula": "query_input_tokens"
              }
            ],
            "queries": [
              {
                "name": "query_input_tokens",
                "data_source": "metrics",
                "query": "avg:aws.bedrock.invocation.input_token_count{service:sre-agent-ecs}"
              }
            ],
            "response_format": "timeseries",
            "style": {
              "palette": "orange",
              "line_type": "solid",
              "line_width": "thin"
            },
            "display_type": "bars"
          },
          {
            "formulas": [
              {
                "alias": "Output Tokens (avg)",
                "formula": "query_output_tokens"
              }
            ],
            "queries": [
              {
                "name": "query_output_tokens",
                "data_source": "metrics",
                "query": "avg:aws.bedrock.invocation.output_token_count{service:sre-agent-ecs}"
              }
            ],
            "response_format": "timeseries",
            "style": {
              "palette": "green",
              "line_type": "solid",
              "line_width": "thin"
            },
            "display_type": "bars"
          },
          {
            "formulas": [
              {
                "alias": "LLM Error Rate (%)",
                "formula": "query_llm_errors / query_llm_total * 100"
              }
            ],
            "queries": [
              {
                "name": "query_llm_errors",
                "data_source": "metrics",
                "query": "sum:aws.bedrock.invocation.client_errors{service:sre-agent-ecs}.as_count()"
              },
              {
                "name": "query_llm_total",
                "data_source": "metrics",
                "query": "sum:aws.bedrock.invocations{service:sre-agent-ecs}.as_count()"
              }
            ],
            "response_format": "timeseries",
            "style": {
              "palette": "red",
              "line_type": "dashed",
              "line_width": "normal"
            },
            "display_type": "line",
            "on_right_yaxis": true
          }
        ],
        "yaxis": {
          "include_zero": true,
          "scale": "linear",
          "label": "Latency (ms) / Token Count"
        },
        "right_yaxis": {
          "include_zero": true,
          "scale": "linear",
          "label": "LLM Error Rate (%)"
        },
        "time": {
          "live_span": "1h"
        }
      },
      "layout": {
        "x": 8,
        "y": 0,
        "width": 4,
        "height": 4
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "definition": {
        "type": "note",
        "content": "## 📋 Live Postmortem – SRE Agent Incident Feed\n\n---\n\n**Last Updated:** _Agent has not reported yet_\n\n**Alert ID:** _pending_\n\n**Service:** `auth-service`\n\n---\n\n### Root Cause\n> _The SRE Agent will populate this section automatically after investigation._\n\n### Evidence\n- Log signals: _pending_\n- Metric signals: _pending_\n- Tool calls executed: _pending_\n\n### Recommended Remediation Steps\n1. _Awaiting agent runbook..._\n2. _Awaiting agent runbook..._\n3. _Awaiting agent runbook..._\n\n---\n\n### How to Update This Widget\nPost the agent's `incident_summary` field here via the [Datadog Dashboard API](https://docs.datadoghq.com/api/latest/dashboards/) or update it manually after each ECS run.\n\n```\nPUT /api/v1/dashboard/{dashboard_id}\n{ \"widgets[2].definition.content\": \"<agent output>\" }\n```\n\n---\n_Powered by Self-Healing Shadow · Amazon Bedrock · ddtrace_",
        "background_color": "white",
        "font_size": "14",
        "text_align": "left",
        "vertical_align": "top",
        "show_tick": false,
        "tick_pos": "50%",
        "tick_edge": "left",
        "has_padding": true
      },
      "layout": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4,
        "width": 12,
        "height": 6
      }
    }
  ]
}
